sec.p:
We all have some power and we all have choices – registered nurses who observe unethical practice must challenge it and follow the procedures to raise and escalate concerns; teachers must work creatively with students enabling them to build the confidence and courage for ethical practice and leadership;
3
 researchers must continue to research the inter-relationship between individual behaviour and organizational culture;
4,5
 and nurse managers must role model ethical practice and challenge aspects of organizations that undermine it. All of us should lobby politicians and policy-makers when initiatives are proposed that undermine the core values and purpose of our profession.
